			<common:synonyms xml:lang="en">Transmissives; Reflectives; Lenses; Filters; Windows; Optical flats; Prisms; Polarizers; Beamsplitters; Wave plates; Fiber optics; Mirrors; Retroreflectors,光学元件毛坯</common:synonyms>
			<classificationInformation>
				<common:classification>
					<common:category level="0">Systems</common:category>
					<common:category level="1">Electrics and electronics</common:category>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Optical components fall into two basic groups: transmissives and reflectives. Transmissives include lenses, filters, windows, optical flats, prisms, polarizers, beamsplitters, wave plates, and fiber optics; reflectives include mirrors and retroreflectors. The performance of all may be enhanced with certain substrates and thin film coatings. Optical components are simple optical elements that are used in the construction of optical systems. They are essential for many applications involving lasers, imaging, spectroscopy, and communication.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">光学组件分为两个基本组：透射组件和反射组件。透射组件包括透镜、滤光片、窗户、光学平板、棱镜、偏振器、分束器、波片和光纤；反射组件包括镜子和反射镜。所有这些的性能都可以通过某些基材和薄膜涂层进行增强。光学组件是用于构建光学系统的简单光学元素。它们对于涉及激光、成像、光谱学和通信的许多应用至关重要。</common:generalComment>
